Homepage: https://github.com/cutefishos/calamares

Package: cutefish-calamares-settings
Architecture: all
Depends: cutefish-calamares (>= 0.5), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Cutefish OS configuration for Calamares installer
 This package provides the Cutefish OS specific configuration files
 for the Calamares system installer.
 .
 It includes:
  - Cutefish OS branding (logos, colors, QML interface)
  - Module configurations for installation process
  - Settings for partitioning, users, packages, etc.
 .
 This package should be installed alongside calamares to provide
 a complete Cutefish OS installation experience.